            954,
            978
        ],
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "使用五向摇杆按键开关机、设置菜单",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            52,
            42,
            757,
            77
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/f0811d53435eb62666cf7f152f208efdc92df6977d22527cb734fb620ccad281.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            221,
            152,
            675,
            429
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显示器的五向摇杆按键可以作为电源键、菜单设置键使用，简单快捷设置显示器。",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            483,
            793,
            502
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "开启与关闭显示器：",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            68,
            510,
            245,
            527
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 开机：向上短按此键，显示器屏幕显示品牌 Logo 后，指示灯点亮，显示器开启。",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            533,
            811,
            552
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显示器工作时，指示灯点亮；显示器无信号输入时，进入待机状态，若菜单中 LED 电源按钮设置为“待机模式时开”，待机状态下指示灯白色闪烁。",
        "bbox": [
            73,
            558,
            932,
            600
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 关机：向上长按此键 2 秒以上，指示灯熄灭，显示器关机。",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            605,
            610,
            623
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设置显示器菜单：",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            68,
            633,
            225,
            650
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "list",
        "sub_type": "text",
        "list_items": [
            "1 显示器开机后，面向屏幕时，向上短按五向摇杆按键，打开显示器设置菜单。",
            "2 在设置菜单界面，根据界面指示的手势操作五向摇杆按键，调节显示器的设置。"
        ],
        "bbox": [
            68,
            662,
            800,
            708
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/b8100acf176393b701c84bcd0032ae186a74f2bb2b6b6018cb8903559ce9c76f.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            719,
            147,
            764
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "：面向屏幕时（下同），向屏幕前、后、左、右按五向摇杆按键，可移动切换选项。",
        "bbox": [
            159,
            747,
            900,
            766
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/c25be6278f9f71746a79909a3a210b55e59f98b75bb7df025a87f7b214ff098c.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            778,
            147,
            822
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "：向左按五向摇杆按键，可返回至上一级菜单或退出菜单。",
        "bbox": [
            159,
            806,
            678,
            824
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/65ebc3f5162c95e918dafe4c54662a92311aa8ccd29305cc838e28ff0e119798.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "content": "",
        "bbox": [
            85,
            835,
            147,
            879
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "：向上或向右按五向摇杆按键，可确认选项。",
        "bbox": [
            159,
            864,
            557,
            882
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "page_number",
        "text": "6 ",
        "bbox": [
            941,
            965,
            954,
            978
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显示器菜单选项 ",
